Content:
Hello everyone

I started my motorcycle blog with trips to cities and countries of Asia, my Instagram profile: leskov.journey, where I share my exciting moments from the roads.
I try to capture all the brightest and most beautiful things.

If you want to see beautiful Moto videos in your feed, you can check out my profile. I am always open to new acquaintances and discussions so I will be glad to receive your comments and feedback.

It is very important for me, I want to develop in the media sphere.
Thank you for your attention and I hope for your support!
